I wrote the complete program to `station/TrainPlatformDemo.java`, compiled with `javac`, and ran it. The driver exercises distinct-platform assignment, a **waiting** train, both queries, the end-exclusive boundary, duplicate-id rejection, zero-length rejection, and out-of-range platform.

